      "instructions": "<div class=\"rich-text-field-label\"><p>Scoring Instructions</p> <ul> <li>Sum the points for each subscale to compute two composite scores.</li> <li>Composite scores are standardized to mean = 0 and SD = 1.</li> <li>Valid answers to at least two questions were necessary to compute each score.</li> </ul> <p>Please see Etter et al. (2000) for a complete description of the statistical analysis used for these questions. Also, Table 5 contains information on assessment of construct validity.</p></div>"
    }
  }
}